      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've ever spent an hour hunting for a single email address, you know the drill. You scroll through LinkedIn, guess at email formats, cross your fingers, and hope the bounce rate stays low. There's a better way to work.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://get.seamless.ai/bh3ilgp4dw5a"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Seamless.AI is a prospecting platform that pulls verified emails and direct phone numbers from LinkedIn in real time. No more guessing. No more outdated databases. Just accurate contact data the moment you need it. I've been using it for months, and it's genuinely changed how I approach outreach. If you want to see what it can do for your pipeline, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "check Seamless.AI here",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — they offer a free plan to start.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Exactly Does Seamless.AI Do?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, Seamless.AI is an AI-powered search engine for B2B contact data. You tell it who you're looking for — a VP of Marketing at a Series B SaaS company, a Director of Operations in healthcare, whatever — and it finds verified email addresses and cell phone numbers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform integrates directly with LinkedIn. You install their browser extension, navigate to a prospect's profile, and Seamless.AI surfaces their contact info on the spot. It also works as a standalone search engine where you can filter by title, company size, industry, location, and dozens of other criteria.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-seamless-ai"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For anyone unfamiliar with the tool, our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "guide on what Seamless.AI is",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " covers the fundamentals in detail.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real-World Use Cases That Drive Results",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Seamless.AI shines. Let me walk through specific scenarios where the tool delivers serious value.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use Case 1: Outbound Sales Teams Building Pipeline Fast",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Picture this: you're an SDR with a quota of 50 new meetings per month. You need to reach decision-makers at mid-market companies, but your CRM contact data is stale. Half the emails bounce. You're burning hours on manual research.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Seamless.AI fixes this. You search for \"Head of Sales\" at companies with 50-500 employees in the tech sector, and within seconds you get a list of verified contacts with direct emails and cell numbers. You export them straight to your CRM or outreach tool and start dialing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One sales team I spoke with told me they cut their prospecting time by 60%. That's hours back every week — hours they now spend on actual conversations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use Case 2: Recruiting Top Talent",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Recruiters face the same problem as salespeople: finding the right person's contact info. Whether you're sourcing engineering leaders for a startup or building a shortlist of CFOs for an executive search, Seamless.AI gives you direct access.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The phone number data is especially valuable here. Senior candidates don't always respond to LinkedIn InMails. A well-timed call to their cell — that gets attention.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use Case 3: Business Development and Partnerships",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "BD teams need to reach specific people at specific companies. Maybe you're pitching a partnership with a logistics firm, or you need to get in front of a product leader at a target account. Seamless.AI lets you identify and contact the exact person you need, not a generic info@ inbox.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use Case 4: Startups Without Enterprise Budgets",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's something I appreciate: Seamless.AI offers a free tier. Startups and solo founders can access real contact data without committing to expensive contracts. You get a limited number of credits per month, but for early-stage teams doing targeted outreach, that's often enough to build meaningful momentum.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-seamless-ai"
